## Task 1.8: MSW setup (opt-in, không đụng existing tests)

Codex review issue #3: existing `jest.setup.js` already has fetch/localStorage mocks. Global MSW with `onUnhandledRequest:'error'` would break the 22 existing tests. Solution: **opt-in MSW** — only tests that explicitly import the enabler get MSW.

